ŘIn loving memory of Ina Lamond (Fry)
born Rosina Maclean
in Ayrshire on 8th Nov 1919
a Mum, Grandma, Great Granny & respected friend
she fell peacefully asleep
at home in Erdington on 14th Dec 2007
A life well led. Thanks be to God

A Celtic Blessing
May the road rise up to meet you
May the wind be always at your back
May the sun shine warm upon your face;
The rains fall soft upon your fields
And until we meet again,
May God hold you in the palm of His hand"Ű
